      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no Danna fazzija wiꞥſch:\nDans irr weens janns Lauwa/\nwiꞥſch iſebks no Bahsana (no\ntreknas Gannibas.)"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no Nawtalis fazzija\nwiꞥſch : Nawtalam irr gaun\nSchehlastibas / ka tam patiks /\nun buhs piſns taKUNGA Sweh-\ntuna / prett Wakkaru un prett\nDeenas-Widdu buhs wiꞥſch ee-\nmantojama Teefa."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no Ahsera fazzija wiꞥſch:\nlaid Ahfers ſwehtihts irr pahr\nteem Dehleem / laid tas fatweem\nBrahteem tabbi patihk / un ee-\nmeirz favas Rahjas eeſch Efjes."
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Dselse un Warsch buhs ap-\npafsch tawahin Kurpehm / un\ntaws Wezzums laid irr / ka taws\nJaunums."
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Zits ne weens Deetws irr\nſtipraks ka Jeschurnna Deews/\nkaß Debbeſi fehd tew par Paligu/\nun ar favu Angstumu Padebbe-\nfis."
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Laid tas muhſchiß Deews\n(tew) weens Dsihwoklis irr / un\nappafsch wiꞥſch Paduffi muh-\nſchigi / un laid wiꞥſch to Eenaid-\nneeku iſdſenn no taws Preek-\nfchas / un fakka: Jsdeldi."
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Israels tad dsihwohs droh-\nschi / Jehkaba Awohts buhs us\nweenu Semmi no Labbibas un\nWihna / un wiꞥſch Debbes pil-\nlehs ar Raffu."
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Lab tew Israels/ kas irr ta"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka tu? tu atpestita Tauta zaun te\nKUNGA / kas taws Palihds\nbas preeſchturrannis Bruwnas\nun kas taws Uswarreschana\nSohbins irr / tapehz ne iſdoſfee\ntaweem Eenaidneekem / bet t\nſtaigati us wiapu Augstumeem."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XXXIV. Nodalla.\nMohsus rahpj us to Neebus Kalnu: 1. Ska-\ntahs to apſohlitu Semmi: 2. Nomirſt 120\nGaddus wezz buhdams: 6/7. Tee Ifraei\nBehrai wiapu aprauda: 8. Un ne ween\ntahds Praueets irr pehz zehlees / kas wiinxan\nbuhtu lihds bijiſeekſch Ifraefa: 10."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ad uſkahpe Mohsus n\nMoaba Klaijumeem u\nto Kalnu Neebus / u\nVisgas Wirz-Gallu / kas pret\nJeriku irr/un tas KUNGS rah-\ndija wiinxam wiſſu Gileada\nSemmi lihds Dannam."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſu Nawtalu/ un Ge-\nwraima un Manassus Semmi\nun to Semmi Juhda lihds ta\ngallejai Juhrai,"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un to Deenas-Widdu\npuſſi/un to Krajumu tahs Gelet\njas Jerikus/ ta Palmu-Pilshah\nta lihds Zoaram."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzij\nus wiinxu: Schi irr ta Semmi-\nko es Ahbrahaman/ Ihsaekam u\nJehkabam ſwehrejs efmu / fazz-\ndams : Tawam Dsinnuman-\nes to dohſchu/ es efmu tew to li-\nzis ar tawahm Azsim redſeht/ be-\nteiw ne buhs us turren pahri ee"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta nomirre Mohsus t\nKUNGA Kalps Moaba Sem-\nme/ pehz ta KUNGA Wahrou"
    }
  ],
